re assigned to the company's newWashington office.andM;Bugos has extensive experience in a wide variety of telecommunicationsendeavors, including a position with Coopers andamp; Lybrand's Strategic ManagementServices, New York.andP;  DST, a member of the Softbridge Group, specializes inthe practical application of information technology for decision support.andO;</TEXT></DOC>